title: S7E08 – "Final Skies" – Scary Stories Told in the Dark
description:
In this episode of Scary Stories Told in the Dark, we bring you four spine-chilling tales from author Elias Witherow, performed by host and narrator Otis Jiry, about accursed clergy, timeless terrors, nightmarish naps, and wicked winds.
